data.description: Are you ready to escape to country living? Do you need a property that has a 2nd home on the same property? This is the country estate that you've been waiting on! This 5 Bedroom / 4 Bathroom and over 3500 Heated Sq Ft home is located in the Otis community. It's placed on approximately 12 acres. The location is 20 minutes from Alexandria and 40 minutes from Leesville. There is a 4 car, 900 square foot carport that offers covered parking and entertaining space. Not only do you get a huge, spacious primary house, but there is also a 990 square foot additional house on the property. This additional home has it's on electrical meter, HVAC system, W/D hookups, and septic system. The primary house not only has 3500+ square feet downstairs and there is also an 800 square foot bonus room upstairs. There is tons of storage in a floored attic space. Parts of the attic could be easily finished for additional rooms and living area. All of the 4 downstair bedrooms are very spacious. The primary bedroom offers a large bathroom suite. Check out that Pantry! The home offers SO much SPACE! The in-ground pool is very large and an allowance will be given in order for it to be made functional. The pool is not functional at this time, virtual staging was used to show potential. Home is priced under appraised value! Your "forever" home awaits!
